shortcomings compared with the more severe interpersonal deficits of B, the unknown stress handling of A, and the moodiness of D.\n**Vote:** Candidate\u202fC\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate C\"}"}
